>> name: Tandoori marinade
>> cuisine: Indian

Combine @yogurt{2%tbsp}, @ground cumin{1%tbsp}, @ground coriander{1%tbsp}, @chilli powder{1%tbsp}, @tumeric{1%tsp}, @curry powder{1%tbsp}, @salt{2%tsp}, @crushed ginger{1%tbsp}, @oil{2%tbsp} and @lemon juice{1} in a bowl. Mix well.

Add meat and marinade for 2 hours.

Cook over charcoal.
